tuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"graphql-result\"><a href=\"#graphql-result\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>GraphQL Result</h2>\n<div class=\"gridsome-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"data\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"allSanityImageAsset\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\">\"edges\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token property\">\"node\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"originalSrc\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;shopify-remote-url>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"downloadedSrc\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              <span class=\"token property\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"file\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token property\">\"mimeType\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"image/jpeg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">//... and all other image properties</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//...</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n"},"repo":{"title":"Remote Image Downloader","content":"<p>Simple plugin to download remote images in gridsome</p>\n","repository":"noxify/gridsome-plugin-remote-image"},"sidebar":{"edges":[{"node":{"category":[{"id":"44306869","title":"Getting started","links":[{"id":"0ce32fc5","title":"Introduction","url":""},{"id":"5d034c15","title":"Configuration","url":"/configuration"}]},{"id":"7ce47ac5","title":"Examples","links":[{"id":"e8a3be2e","title":"Filesystem","url":"/example-filesystem"},{"id":"678d13ac","title":"Contentful","url":"/example-contentful"},{"id":"7be26776","title":"Sanity","url":"/example-sanity"},{"id":"da5d77d8","title":"Shopify","url":"/example-shopify"}]}]}}]}},"context":{"id":"1d08269639e2a78f580d56ae44640475","plugin":"gridsome-plugin-remote-image","pluginId":"gridsome-plugin-remote-image"}}